{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23031.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day06.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime05","chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-1"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]What do you mean?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-2"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Obviously, you're lackin' firepower."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":1,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-3"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Firepower?"},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-4"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Mabayu might be able to see the future,@but those scissors don't do much damage."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-5"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]W-well, yeah..."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-6"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Same sort of thing with Homura."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]The ability to stop time is powerful, but@you can't directly attack enemies with it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":101,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-8"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]That's...certainly true."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-9"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]In that regard, I'm pretty confident@in my own firepower."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-10"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But there's only so much I can do@on my own."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-11"},{"eyeClose":0,"id":200601}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I won't recruit any more allies."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-12"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Adding uncertainties only makes@coordination difficult."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Yeah, I get that."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-14"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's why I'm tryin' to make some@other suggestions."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-15"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Such as...?"},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-16"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Well, you go around usin' stuff@like guns and explosives, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You're basically using your magic@to multiply physical firepower."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-18"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, what if you made that physical part@more powerful?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-19"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I see...@In other words?"},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You've got the ability to stop time, so you@can just walk right into military bases."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-21"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Tanks, fighter jets, whatever.@It's all free for the taking."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":400,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-22"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Huh?@A-are you...serious?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-23"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What, are ya chickenin' out now?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-24"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...No."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-25"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Um, M-Miss Akemi?!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200201,"motion":101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-26"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I appreciate it."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-26b"},{"id":200902,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It's not that I hadn't considered it before..."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-27"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But it wasn't something I could@convince myself to do on my own."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-28"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I would have wasted an unnecessary amount@of time to arrive at the same conclusion."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-29"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Wait, so you mean...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-30"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]That's right. We'll strike back at@Walpurgisnacht with as much@firepower as possible."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-31"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]And to do that, there needs to be@enough time to transport those weapons..."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-32"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]We're going to need a lot of Grief Seeds."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-33"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You're serious about this..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":1,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-34"},{"id":200201,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Well. There's still no tellin'@if that'll be enough."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-35"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But it should improve the odds@compared to how things are now..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-36"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Heh, things are startin' to get@interesting."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-37"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Let's get to business then.@I have a favor to ask you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913106-040-38"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Sure, I'm all ears.@What've you got for me next?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
